:markdown-it
  The mobile drawer section contains the navigation and all
  your app-wide actions. It provides a simple container that you
  can fill according to the individual needs of your app.

  The section is usually only available on small viewports, where
  room is scarce. It can be opened using the burger button.
  The drawer-behavior is part of the
  [Site Component](/components/site.html "Site Component"), which
  is the parent component of this one.

