  # Overview
  
  The mobile drawer section is totally flexible. It only provides
  the container for your [Grid](/fundamentals/layout/grid.html "Grid System")
  with some special styling for certain child components.
  
  It usually contains a
  [Mobile Menu](/components/mobile-menu.html "Mobile Menu") and some
  [Buttons](/components/button.html "Buttons").

